  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>화장품 단상자</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92edac12-8000-4505-857f-c3c8b48c14c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0e4d2576-0fb4-4b78-aaa5-8b1c6f0b6ad6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224003704268/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">화장품 단상자</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">단상자를 사용하는 업종 중에 가장 많은 업종이 화장품 업체일 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-41e517dc-b4e5-45a1-94f3-7bfd95dd738e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-33c0e440-d42e-49ac-9016-d161c92be710\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3819d9f-546a-4252-8153-646ceef65f9b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2e6225d5-3ce9-4a7b-a0dd-f9f3f040fc85\" style=\"color:#555555;\">화장품 단상자는 가장 많이 사용되는 박스이기도 하고 여러 가지 후가공을 넣어서 작업하더라도 싸바리나 합지 박스에 비해 단가도 상대적으로 저렴하게 제작을 할 수 있기 때문에 거의 95% 이상이 단상자 형태로 만들고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50214f87-95ad-4d2d-95e1-7286de037d37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d0d74fb5-d7bc-45b2-8825-fc777bb06eb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6c9d7362-4617-4793-b939-19c4e61c05c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-163df3f0-c10b-4dcc-9bc1-3cea1917b250\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그렇다면 단상자 중에 위 향수병에 가장 잘 어울리는 패키지와 후공정은 어떤 것일까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8d50278d-d525-45af-af19-55f1860b9128\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56ffa20b-7755-4fe7-9e53-8309edeb94d3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b3224943-dcb4-4e5e-812b-f9d3a185e837\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-78e67966-6dab-467e-a4fb-ff3187ff4289\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오늘은 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-296a17c7-31a0-414d-b999-68fad801c0d5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>고급스러운 후공정 방법</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df7df3a7-37f0-495d-a0af-603d2a9e9b0c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 소개합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c3acea34-370e-42f5-9ba6-ca68b1169542\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-145d4943-681f-45bb-a53b-e32768949363\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f79ca8d-7e9d-4df8-b997-08a054a10ab9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-6d484cd9-48c0-4372-84f8-85646d3c23df\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>별색인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6bafc89a-46bc-4c9d-82a5-927a43292bd8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7b47a5b9-bb46-427d-a0bf-41a0bafb14a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4140197-5ca7-438f-aa39-acfd4f0a1145\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c83c6949-d4e2-45a2-a303-ee1b2b0587a3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>화장품 패키지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d69b8add-888c-4847-a5cf-2802c6cd3025\" style=\"color:#555555;\">는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-64bebda9-b2a0-4bf9-9982-6fe3899787a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>브랜드 컬러</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c326a6a6-4892-49dd-8c90-796f9e866f4b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가 매우 중요합니다. 4도로 CMYK를 표현하기보다는 별색 컬러로 진행하는 것이 훨씬 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e75a6500-71e9-4813-a4d7-cbede4c843d0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:768px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224003704268/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0ecf0282-6b90-4b05-aa8e-3a6d3edbc62f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1b442ec1-4e11-4ef6-b736-6c2dbd99e017\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-21366d0f-75d6-44b7-a9f8-9d6cb2fb78b3\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">이런 컬러를 4도 인쇄로 진행하면 추후 재발주에 반드시 색상이 변하게 되어 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8676eb58-bcb9-42ba-9503-9bf8e4d2b5b8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-36a61faf-4c98-4a30-a24e-c45204244ead\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8535c811-4e66-4916-acd6-144d472e4933\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-252d5657-3fb6-4c89-994f-c611555bca44\" style=\"color:#555555;\">특히 초콜릿 색상이나 암녹색은 CMYK 컬로 인쇄하면 색상이 통일되게 나오기 어렵습니다. 물론 별색이라고 해도 색상이 100% 일치하게 나오지는 않습니다. 하지만 CMYK 인쇄보다는 훨씬 더 통일된 컬러를 구현할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b48f7b28-7fcc-4e6e-a937-cf840b26b9d4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:279px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224003704268/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1790ea38-d569-4745-bfa0-a516360f8bbe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c85edf43-091c-4318-992e-19cae8b20c02\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-d97b8e21-cf5d-496c-9d24-bfc40fd389a0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>PANTONE 384 C로</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e1348690-ddf9-4f9e-a69c-f59cca6a8d5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 작업하면 별색으로 진행하겠다는 의미입니다. 이렇게 브랜드 컬러는 팬턴 컬러로 진행하면 더 통일된 색상으로 진행이 가능합니다. 별색으로 진행하기 위해서는 팬턴 컬러 번호를 인쇄업체에 알려주고 인쇄하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b231543c-709c-417d-a3ab-10259887fa81\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8c1fd3ad-495e-4336-bfb6-6fdff7e85314\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-63b4f320-fe50-4d8d-b007-9e0ca868d077\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c946032-98f5-4eb6-997d-6fed30f1055a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 특히 브랜드 컬러는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-18e7297e-56ac-45b6-8df1-c20d25560b4e\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>감리</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8168e45e-e5a0-496f-9d54-774dc70e40ac\" style=\"color:#555555;\">를 진행하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-56188d9c-cd17-4c98-b474-7cfde3ab1410\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-34f99f11-fe95-4a62-b9ce-900d110c5b7b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8b1aafae-c693-4526-bed2-38cc5c500836\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8187e178-5efe-4c4d-bff9-249afa89a723\" style=\"color:#555555;\">감리는 클라이언트가 색상을 인쇄 기장님과 함께 맞춰가는 작업입니다. 감리를 고객 여러분께서 경험해 보셨는지 몰라도 쉬울 수도 있고 되게 까다로운 작업을 수도 있습니다. 한번 경험해 보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6211d002-8a7c-48be-ab06-0bc0f0371cd4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f7f1b39c-b42b-4a4a-abc9-4d927cdcfaaf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3fc003d-0ad6-45d4-aa2f-68d1d5318b29\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8a20f981-1c7d-4989-b6ce-8ebc6dbd8f7c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">통상 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4d3d3455-d9cd-405a-b973-097693460e3c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>감리비용</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e96f62cd-65fd-4167-8b60-8517f0a69da1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">을 받는 것이 일반적입니다. 하지만 큰 물량인 경우 감리를 시행하므로 감리비용을 인쇄 제작비에 포함시키는 경우가 많습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a069b3a-9d15-4246-af57-0d32a7bf8603\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b367fd91-ccce-4788-8869-1acd4947d153\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c56426bb-1db5-4ed0-ade9-2a6aeb980afd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-937a3d9f-f9e8-41a9-9388-7307f5203875\" style=\"color:#555555;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 경우에 따라 감리를 시행하고 있습니다. 물론 여러 가지 조건이 있습니다. 이 부분은 반드시 상담을 통해 결정합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4c8d168f-744e-4703-91d1-ec3f07c150e3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4fb5b86b-e6f0-4aec-b800-3f464598d7fe\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8255687f-5e90-4952-bfe1-aae23eb22e0a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e689adc7-9dda-419e-b324-b9893fa7abc6\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>박인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9954fba0-322f-4f5e-8055-ecff2f159e4a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ce08cb91-0e60-4cc4-87ea-84def48c22c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-235d5804-2b8e-4b66-bdf3-9ae1646be731\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e487784e-41ec-4a35-81e2-43d399271a08\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고급 화장품에서 가장 많이 사용되는 후공정입니다. 금박이나 은박 또는 다른 종류의 박인쇄가 많이 사용됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e955430a-fe13-45aa-b6ba-3806ecc96438\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/224003704268/003.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-18fe2c5f-a912-4d19-a63f-8ecaaddd9ca6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-99974a63-b0c9-4ab7-83b7-6a3ab1c1b20c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e3c38d55-13d0-45c6-97c0-264d6b318061\" style=\"color:#555555;\">고객 여러분은 박종류가 얼마나 많은지는 아실까요? 언제 한번 블로그로 박인쇄의 종류에 대해 알려드리도록 하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5c8276b6-227b-4bc3-aa17-6c8905c14062\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0e07edac-c084-41fe-a9d6-e2e804fb84a0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cbe4a67d-6d68-46b8-a0b6-edfeb7d5c8ce\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-46efc6ea-460b-4fb8-95f2-6229f3c431b9\" style=\"color:#0078cb;\"><b>형압</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8cbe5f71-3778-497b-9ca9-13cabb9162b0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cdc2de7b-e614-4abb-a399-c3e3e085114b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c44dbc6-f070-45b7-b372-b0f7fb676b6a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8e7ade45-7702-4e1f-9d25-b3b23ea51894\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오목이나 볼록으로 종이를 눌러 튀어나오도록 하는 기법입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bc959f46-d5a7-4200-a087-df4d868ffc53\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19d0cee5-dea4-4b00-9b39-a839c493f8f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd8483c0-7706-4386-b0c0-04fccb992750\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9ee26b15-fb9e-48d5-95a9-fbc5cd7efecd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-35f05d65-16f2-4da6-b3ea-d7f10cdbcb0c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이후 다른 후공정이나 부족한 부분의 글을 계속 작성하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cfc5ff9-3fb1-4074-a7cd-ca5e7e5ee68d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-86a35802-9595-4584-97b1-a58d61496755\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
